# Svelte Frontend

## Structure

```
apps/host-desktop/src/
├── App.svelte              — Root component
├── components/
│   ├── Settings.svelte     — Configuration panel (sensitivity, curve, mode, friction)
│   └── StatusBar.svelte    — Connection status, latency indicator
└── main.ts                 — Svelte mount entry point
```

## Rules

- Svelte **5** with runes (`$state`, `$derived`, `$effect`) — no legacy `$:` reactive statements
- TypeScript for all `.ts` files
- Tauri IPC: use `@tauri-apps/api` invoke for Rust commands (`get_config`, `save_config`)
- Vite 6 dev server on port **1420** (configured in `vite.config.ts`)
- Keep UI minimal — this is a system tray app, not a full window app
- Settings map 1:1 to `AppConfig` Rust struct fields
